title: OTP/TOTP pairing flow for channel access control
---
Replace static chat-ID allowlists with 6-digit TOTP pairing handshake. One-time code flow → bearer token with time-window validation. More secure than static allowlists for ephemeral/mobile users; chat IDs can leak. Pilot with Telegram channel, extend to others. Needs TOTP crypto + config state machine. Integration placement.